    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><iframe frameborder="no" border="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" width="98%" height="86" src="//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=1332217066&auto=1&height=66"></iframe><h3><span id="品令茶词">品令·茶词</span></h3><h6><span id="黄庭坚宋">黄庭坚[宋]</span></h6><p>凤舞团团饼。恨分破、教孤令。金渠体净，只轮慢碾，玉尘光莹。汤响松风，早减了、二分酒病。<br>味浓香永。醉乡路、成佳境。恰如灯下，故人万里，归来对影。口不能言，心下快活自省。</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
