    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>小胖说今天星巴克买一送一</p><p><img lazyload src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Xcloud1988/Pix@master/images/drink1.aedjit2e33k.jpg"></p><p>味道还不错，今天我也发现了羊毛，和小胖一起在踩雷的边缘勇敢前进。</p><p><img lazyload src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Xcloud1988/Pix@master/images/drink2.6c8xolgs0b00.jpg"></p><p>小胖的，哎嘿，就没有我拍的好看</p><p><img lazyload src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Xcloud1988/Pix@master/images/drink8.5b97k57ziuc0.jpg"></p><p>台风来了！台风来了！冒着生命不可承受之风去拿Tims。嗯么，口感还是不错的，这波血赚。</p><p>喝太快，没拍。这是来自另一天的Tims和可颂。</p><p><img lazyload src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Xcloud1988/Pix@master/images/drink4.64kclxm2beo0.jpg"></p><p>今天喝奶茶，被小胖忽悠扔掉盖子，头顶凉凉</p><p><img lazyload src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Xcloud1988/Pix@master/images/drink7.6af5tjtwhx40.jpg"></p><p>终于还是踩雷了，把这段时间来的第一次交给了瑞幸。杨梅，甜到牙疼，食之头疼，弃之可惜。</p><p>噢噢噢，还有我的airpods小皮肤。</p><p><img lazyload src="/images/loading.svg" data-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Xcloud1988/Pix@master/images/drink3.2021t34o9vs0.jpg"></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
